---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { site } from '../config';
---
<Layout
  title={`Privacy Policy — ${site.name}`}
  description="How Nemi Digital Agency collects, uses and protects your personal information."
>
  <section class="py-16">
    <article class="container-narrow max-w-3xl prose prose-slate">
      <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="heading mt-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-500">Last updated: July 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-ink-700 leading-relaxed text-[15px]">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">1. Who we are</h2>
        <p>{site.name} ("we", "us", "our") is a digital design & development agency based in Bundelkhand, Uttar Pradesh, India. This policy explains how we collect and use information when you visit our website or contact us.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">2. Information we collect</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Information you give us:</strong> name, email, company and message when you submit the contact form.</li>
          <li><strong>Automatically collected information:</strong> IP address, browser type, referring pages, and pages visited — via standard server logs and analytics (if enabled).</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">3. How we use it</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>To reply to your inquiries and deliver the services you requested.</li>
          <li>To improve the website (debugging, performance, content relevance).</li>
          <li>To send occasional updates about our work, only if you opt in.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We never sell your data. We never share it with third parties for marketing.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">4. Services we use</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Netlify:</strong> hosting and form processing. See <a href="https://www.netlify.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Netlify's privacy policy</a>.</li>
          <li><strong>Resend:</strong> transactional email delivery for contact form notifications. See <a href="https://resend.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Resend's privacy policy</a>.</li>
          <li><strong>Google Fonts:</strong> loaded via Google's CDN; Google may log the request.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">5. Data retention</h2>
        <p>Contact form submissions are retained for up to 24 months so we can reference past conversations, then deleted or anonymized upon request.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">6. Your rights</h2>
        <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data at any time by emailing <a href="mailto:hello@nemidigital.agency" class="text-brand-600 hover:underline">hello@nemidigital.agency</a>. We respond within 7 days.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">7. Cookies</h2>
        <p>This site does not use tracking cookies. Netlify and our host may set technical cookies required for security and form submission.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">8. Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about this policy? Email us at <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`} class="text-brand-600 hover:underline">{site.email}</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h2 { margin-top: 2.5rem; }
</style>
